titulo: Artificial Generative AI Revolutionizes Content Creation
descripcion: Generative AI tools like ChatGPT and DALL-E are transforming the way text, images and videos are created, making it easier to quickly produce customized content.

titulo: Google Unveils New AI to Improve Searches
descripcion: Google launched an update to its search engine with advanced AI that offers more contextual results and direct answers, improving the user experience.
